## Lightweight Threads
Goroutines are functions that run concurrently with other functions.

```go
func say(text string) {
    fmt.Println(text)
}

func main() {
    go say("World")  // Runs in background
    say("Hello")     // Runs immediately
    time.Sleep(time.Second) // Wait for goroutine to finish
}
```

Goroutines are cheap — you can easily run thousands of them.

